{"tid":2393252,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"非法集結案警員稱拍攝不到磚頭只因太小 辯方：除非沙粒咁細","createTime":"2021-02-03T10:31:49.000Z","updateTime":"2021-02-03T14:22:11.000Z","uid":56115,"like":1,"dislike":13,"uniUserReply":13,"replies":[{"pid":"1d78e70e987b62f4b2ec2391f0894ef951b8538f","tid":2393252,"uid":56115,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-02-03T10:31:49.000Z","msg":"前年10月1日示威者「遍地開花」，多區有示威活動，其中9名男女被指當日在黃大仙非法集結，案件今日在西九龍裁判法院續審。辯方質疑，<span class=\"red\">涉嫌與同袍「夾口供」的警員所供稱的示威者位置及堵路範圍均與片段顯示不符</span>，質問：「何解你要虛構不存在嘅嘢呢？」<span class=\"red\">警員回應稱只因磚頭太細而且鐵欄貼在地下</span>，才令鏡頭未能清楚拍攝現場實況。而<span class=\"red\">另一名被指夾口供的警員承認，兩人落口供的時間及地點均一樣，並且隸屬同一組別，辦公室位處同一樓層，並由同一個督察帶領。</span><br />\n<br />\n辯方播放當日警方拍攝片段，指片段顯示警方在嗇色園外時，警方前方百多米已無人，看不到有200人聚集，亦見不到地面有警員所指的雜物，「條片大家都睇到嘞，已經不容爭辯。我想問嘅係，何解你要虛構不存在嘅嘢呢？」<br />\n<br />\n羅卻稱「磚頭太細，鏡頭可能影得唔清楚咗」。辯方大狀不滿謂：「除非磚頭係沙粒咁細啫。」至於鐵欄位置，羅則稱「影唔到囉，鐵欄貼喺地下嘛」<br />\n<br />\n大狀指出，兩人記錄整個警方推進過程的段落「完美地一樣」 。鄭同意，但否認兩人抄寫口供，強調「我冇睇過佢份口供」。"},{"pid":"30b1d22755cc56f01c415da7c0d13f8f043ae061","tid":2393252,"uid":56115,"like":1,"dislike":7,"score":-6,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-02-03T10:31:56.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://hk.appledaily.com/local/20210203/R3KEKVLUYVEJHAIF2G5GJMSUQY/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Flocal%2F20210203%2FR3KEKVLUYVEJHAIF2G5GJMSUQY%2F&d=f02Xtm2mX5FaAGCExHUdjXvcSryOYOd41eK7VOq09cM%3D&h=7fe2ab91\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Flocal%2F20210203%2FR3KEKVLUYVEJHAIF2G5GJMSUQY%2F&h=ec26e8b0\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://hk.appledaily.com/local/20210203/R3KEKVLUYVEJHAIF2G5GJMSUQY/</a>"},{"pid":"6467424d09f699695db2706ae3e5cb535c7c350d","tid":2393252,"uid":191588,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-02-03T10:33:14.000Z","msg":"Push"},{"pid":"1a5cecd3caa7701b16d34895f9c0f68fbda60ee2","tid":2393252,"uid":39710,"like":17,"dislike":0,"score":17,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-02-03T10:34:21.000Z","msg":"日撚日上庭俾假證供"},{"pid":"bd6dd031f1af25284798b372ad064bdf66818c11","tid":2393252,"uid":292585,"like":13,"dislike":0,"score":13,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-02-03T10:36:33.000Z","msg":"磚頭同石仔係咪唔識分<br />\n之前指鹿為馬 今日炮艇充舢舨<br />\n黑警又再次刷新我三觀"},{"pid":"2e20309e25f695fc0c622c7349cb507cfbd45c46","tid":2393252,"uid":27122,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-02-03T10:58:19.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"2a2e75dcb8066db1c8674c9b24d7eaeac7a208c7","tid":2393252,"uid":56115,"like":1,"dislike":2,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-02-03T11:07:43.000Z","msg":"控方詢問<span class=\"red\">警察有何行動</span>，鄭聽錯成「示威者有何行動」，稱<span class=\"red\">「叫囂、掟雜物」</span>。鄭的回答引起律師及公眾席人士竊笑，控方重問後，鄭才改稱警方向前推進。<br />\n<br />\n辯方質疑片段與警員供詞不符，問鄭：「何解你同你同事都見到嘅嘢，我哋冇人（從片中）見到？」鄭尚未回答，裁判官黃士翔指其問題不夠客觀，「你自己睇唔到，唔代表其他人睇唔到」。案件明天續審。<a href=\"https://www.thestandnews.com/court/10-1-%E9%BB%83%E5%A4%A7%E4%BB%99-%E8%AD%A6%E7%A8%B1%E9%BB%91%E8%A1%A3%E4%BA%BA%E6%94%BE%E9%9B%9C%E7%89%A9%E5%9C%A8%E9%A6%AC%E8%B7%AF-%E8%BE%AF%E6%96%B9%E8%B3%AA%E7%96%91%E8%88%87%E7%89%87%E4%B8%8D%E7%AC%A6-%E6%94%9D%E9%8C%84%E8%AD%A6-%E7%A3%9A%E9%A0%AD%E5%A4%AA%E7%B4%B0%E5%BD%B1%E5%94%94%E5%88%B0/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.thestandnews.com%2Fcourt%2F10-1-%25E9%25BB%2583%25E5%25A4%25A7%25E4%25BB%2599-%25E8%25AD%25A6%25E7%25A8%25B1%25E9%25BB%2591%25E8%25A1%25A3%25E4%25BA%25BA%25E6%2594%25BE%25E9%259B%259C%25E7%2589%25A9%25E5%259C%25A8%25E9%25A6%25AC%25E8%25B7%25AF-%25E8%25BE%25AF%25E6%2596%25B9%25E8%25B3%25AA%25E7%2596%2591%25E8%2588%2587%25E7%2589%2587%25E4%25B8%258D%25E7%25AC%25A6-%25E6%2594%259D%25E9%258C%2584%25E8%25AD%25A6-%25E7%25A3%259A%25E9%25A0%25AD%25E5%25A4%25AA%25E7%25B4%25B0%25E5%25BD%25B1%25E5%2594%2594%25E5%2588%25B0%2F&d=f02Xtm2mX5FaAGCExHUdjXvcSryOYOd41eK7VOq09cM%3D&h=a32a4620\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fw